{"root":{"data":{"id":"d2kmvjzclns0","created":1720490203166,"text":"无人机管理系统"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kmvu4hj4o0","created":1720490225244,"text":"1.用户登录","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kncx2wodc0","created":1720491563870,"text":"用户身份验证","note":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knguknqgg0","created":1720491871870,"text":"账号错误"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knh90ikmw0","created":1720491903303,"text":"密码错误"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knhbz22ww0","created":1720491909746,"text":"条件错误","note":"如 二维码刷新失败、token更新失败、界面刷新异常"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knrq9pvbs0","created":1720492724507,"text":"注册密码确认异常"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knd0jt6rs0","created":1720491571422,"text":"用户登录界面","note":"功能描述：用户输入用户名和密码后，系统通过比对数据库中的信息来验证用户的身份。\n执行条件：用户输入用户名和密码，并点击登录按钮。\n执行结果：如果验证成功，用户将进入系统主界面；如果验证失败，系统将显示错误消息，并允许用户重新输入。","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knmx6v9200","created":1720492347751,"text":"登录账号"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knn1oky340","created":1720492357529,"text":"登录密码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knn5z7rj40","created":1720492366879,"text":"登录按钮"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kno4phwcg0","created":1720492442479,"text":"记住密码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knp2zidso0","created":1720492517095,"text":"跳转注册"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2kndmcz9fk0","created":1720491618899,"text":"用户注册界面","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knpddo1ts0","created":1720492539719,"text":"注册账号"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knq1po9eg0","created":1720492592688,"text":"注册密码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knq5zxvs00","created":1720492602016,"text":"注册密码确认"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knqkdhsc80","created":1720492633310,"text":"注册按钮"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knqootqo80","created":1720492642703,"text":"跳转登录"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knnva0bmw0","created":1720492421952,"text":"退出登录"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knsk43n9s0","created":1720492789471,"text":"2.地图导航"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2ko9sgwt740","created":1720494139850,"text":"地图展示界面","note":"功能描述：通过地图的形式直观展示电力设备的地理位置、运行状态、巡检路径等信息。\n执行条件：系统实时或定期从电力巡检设备、传感器等数据源接收数据。\n执行结果：用户可以在地图界面上清晰地看到电力设备的分布情况、运行状态以及巡检路径等信息。","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kor2iah6g0","created":1720495493892,"text":"地图放大"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolsi8fkw0","created":1720495080300,"text":"地图缩小"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2komw0lgl40","created":1720495166305,"text":"距离测量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kon7giq8w0","created":1720495191212,"text":"面积测量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2koqwjjvkg0","created":1720495480908,"text":"角度计算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kp0njzwns0","created":1720496244985,"text":"2D/3D切换","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kp0ukm1v40","created":1720496260260,"text":"2D地图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kp0yr1qvs0","created":1720496269356,"text":"3D地图"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2koa5cwo7c0","created":1720494167906,"text":"地图定位","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kol8aeo680","created":1720495036291,"text":"指南针"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolbvroiw0","created":1720495044113,"text":"起点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2komlkhttc0","created":1720495143564,"text":"分支点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kom83n4a00","created":1720495114246,"text":"终点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolxmapc80","created":1720495091430,"text":"目标点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2konm05ou80","created":1720495222875,"text":"标点定位","note":"功能描述：显示经纬度，如（经纬度：[ 114.54847,38.042804 ]）。\n执行条件：鼠标先点击“标点定位”按钮（最好为单选按钮），然后鼠标左键点击地图某处位置。\n执行结果：标点定位成功后上方显示经纬度，右上方显示关闭按钮。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knsximheo0","created":1720492818647,"text":"3.照片研究","priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kpewkda4w0","created":1720497361697,"text":"4.视频管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kpfatobu80","created":1720497392735,"text":"5.巡检航线"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kpfgsf8yo0","created":1720497405720,"text":"6.设备管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kpfl3q0800","created":1720497415110,"text":"7."},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}